##Â zonaris 

Interested in staking your DATA but don't have the time or know-how? 

zonaris.io enables the Streamr Community to set up nodes in one-click without hassle or code. Start by using the one-month free trial. 

To start a broker node using zonaris, simply create an account (with a one-month free trial) and get access to the dashboard. Once you have an account, select how many nodes you would like to start, enter your wallet address(es), and then click "deploy."

After you have deployed the node(s), effortlessly manage and check on DATA earnings any time. 

There is no minimum or maximum amount of nodes you can have in the dashboard. 
